  "analyst_note": "Splunk Enterprise multiple vulnerabilities including XSS, CSRF, and code execution. Port 8089 is the Splunk management REST API (may not require auth on older versions). Port 8000 is the web UI. The /services/server/info endpoint returns JSON with version. Fixed: 5.0.16, 6.0.12, 6.1.11, 6.2.11, 6.3.6, 6.4.2.",
